    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <description>Prism provides an implementation of a collection of design patterns that are helpful in writing well structured and maintainable XAML applications, including MVVM, dependency injection, commanding, event aggregation, and more. Prism's core functionality is a shared code base in a Portable Class Library targeting these platforms; WPF, Windows 10 UWP, Xamarin Forms and Perspex. Features that need to be platform specific are implemented in the respective libraries for the target platform. Prism for Perspex.Desktop helps you more easily design and build rich, flexible, and easy to maintain Perspex.Desktop applications.</description>
    <summary>Prism libraries related to user interface composition, regions, and modularity for WPF.</summary>
    <releaseNotes>$releaseNotes$</releaseNotes>
    <language>en-US</language>
    <tags>prism mvvm xamarin uwp uap xaml wpf perspex autofac</tags>
